Bubo Defense team,

The Naval Systems Group is releasing RFP-2026-0417 for integration of a
secure tactical communications relay into our existing field kits. This
is a follow-on to the FY25 pilot and is available under the OASIS+
contract vehicle, which we understand Bubo Defense holds.

Estimated contract value is $2.4M over 18 months. Proposals are due in
21 days (by July 27, 2026). Given your team's incumbency on the FY25
pilot, we believe you're well positioned to respond.

Please confirm intent to bid and let us know if you have any questions
about the attached statement of work.

